OL,3,CMan beat girlfriend to death after
OL,4,Cargument over her use of social media
OL,6,FA man from Edenbridge has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of murdering his girlfriend
OL,8,Fafter he beat her to death during an
OL,9,Fargument.
OL,11,FHuseyin Kalyoncu was arrested by Kent
OL,12,FPolice on 5 May 2024 after Sonia
OL,13,FParker was found unconscious at their
OL,14,Fhome in Styles Close, after a dispute
OL,15,Fover her use of WhatsApp.
OL,17,FThe 33-year-old admitted to officers
OL,18,Fat the scene that in the days before
OL,19,Fhe had repeatedly assaulted his
OL,20,Fgirlfriend out of jealousy over her
OL,21,Fsocial media use.
