OL,3,CMan beat girlfriend to death after
OL,4,Cargument over her use of social media
OL,6,FDuring what proved to be their final
OL,7,Fdisagreement, Ms Parker was knocked
OL,8,Funconscious following a sustained
OL,9,Fassault at the hands of Kalyoncu.
OL,11,FParamedics attempted to revive the 51-
OL,12,Fyear-old, but she was pronounced
OL,13,Fdeceased shortly after. Her attacker
OL,14,Fwas arrested in connection to her
OL,15,Fdeath and later charged with murder.
OL,17,FKalyoncu was remanded in custody and
OL,18,Fappeared before Maidstone Crown Court
OL,19,Fon 13 June 2024, where he denied the
OL,20,Fcharge.
