OL,3,CMan beat girlfriend to death after
OL,4,Cargument over her use of social media
OL,6,FHe later admitted to manslaughter,
OL,7,Fwhen he returned to court for trial on
OL,8,FMonday 21 October.
OL,10,FDuring the trial, the court heard how
OL,11,FMs Parker died from a combination of
OL,12,Fcatastrophic injuries to her head and
OL,13,Ftorso after the perpetrator repeatedly
OL,14,Fstruck her with extreme force.
OL,16,FIn total, the victim suffered 69 marks
OL,17,Fto her body, internal bruising, damage
OL,18,Fto her liver and spleen, five
OL,19,Ffractured back bones, and 19 fractures
OL,20,Fto her ribs and chest.
