OL,6,F'Kalyoncu subjected Sonia to a
OL,7,Fsustained campaign of violence. 'He
OL,8,Fabused the woman he was meant to love
OL,9,Fand protect. He physically punished
OL,10,Fher behind closed doors for run-of-the-
OL,11,Fmill actions others take for granted,
OL,12,Fsuch as using social media or talking
OL,13,Fto friends.'The jury were left with no
OL,14,Fother choice but to find him
OL,15,Fresponsible for Sonia's untimely
OL,16,Fdeath. 'I hope the conviction provides
OL,17,FSonia's family and friends with some
OL,18,Fcomfort that Sonia's killer will see a
OL,19,Fsignificant custodial sentence as
OL,20,Fconsequence for his abhorrent
OL,21,Fbehaviour.'
